Package: aggmunicipality
Title: Aggregate Small Polygons Until a Population Threshold
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Elsa", "Farinella", , "elsa.farinella@epfl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Iteratively merges contiguous spatial units (e.g. municipalities,
    districts) until every group meets a minimum population threshold.
